[Katanga is one of the provinces of the Democratic Republic of the Congo (Congo DR), formerly Zaire. Katanga's regional capital is Lubumbashi. Its area, at 497 000 sq km, is larger than California and 16 times larger than Belgium. Farming and ranching are carried out on the Katanga Plateau. The eastern part of the province is a rich mining region that supplies cobalt, copper, tin, radium, uranium, and diamonds.

A map of the provinces of Congo DR can be accessed at: http://www.emapsworld.com/democratic-republic-of-congo-provinces-map.html. - Mod.CP

